title: ZEBRA PRINT COSMETIC/JEWELRY TRAIN CASE
description:
We at DBROTH had fashion, organization and gift giving in mind when we designed these beautiful cosmetic/jewelry train cases. A must-have for organizing and storing all your beauty essentials as well as your fine and costume jewlelry. Our 
zebra print design is the only one of it's kind 
seen on Amazon and made especially for the 
Amazon customer. Features: Fashion zebra 
print, flocked velveteen interior (black), 2
removable tray drawers, 2 extendable trays with larger inner tray, side holders-8 on each side and vanity mirror. Organize and store eye liner, masacara, blush, foundation, 
nail polish, make up brushes, lip sticks, eye liner, tweezers, razors, cotton balls, 
creams, lotions as well as rings, watches, pins, earrings, necklaces and so much more. Great for travel or display on your home dresser. High Quality Aluminum Frame With Reinforced Steel Corners and carry handle. Look for our Leopard Print and Red Faux Leather Grain Alligator Styles also sold on Amazon. Each Measures: 11 1/2"L x 8.1/2"H x 7" W (closed) and 24"L x 13 1/2"H x 9"W (open). Includes 2 keys for 2 locks.

title: Conair Curl Fusion Ionic Ceramic Styler Hair Dryer
description: Get flawless curls with the Conair 1800 watt curl fusion ionic ceramic styler. The unique design diffuses airflow to gently dry and enhance your hair's natural curls and waves. Ionic technolgy gives your hair shine and controls frizz. Ceramic technology keeps your hair looking healthy by pretventing heat damage. Plus, a volume lift attachment is included to help define natural curls and texture.
